Class Node<E>

java.lang.Object
Node<E>
Type Parameters:
E - Node's Element
public class Node<E> extends Object
Basic Node class to be used with the DoublyLinkedList Each node contains an element, the next node, and the previous node, and has methods to change each
Version:
1.0, 10/13/23
Author:
Nicholas Un
